snippet.title: Summerhouse - Official Announcement Trailer | Wholesome Snack December 2023
snippet.description: Get ready to build a neighborhood of tiny, adorable lived-in houses in various locations, and learn more about this cozy building game in this announcement trailer for Summerhouse. Summerhouse will be available in 2024 on PC, and a demo is available now on Steam.
